Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:32.43,Campus Common,美鈴,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:32.43,Campus Common,美鈴,0,0,0,,言われなくても……\n次は1位を取りますよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:38.35,Campus Common,美鈴,0,0,0,,
